{"tid":2246431,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"麥佳亞飽受批評，但比他強的又有幾個？","createTime":"2020-10-17T05:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T05:38:49.000Z","uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"926bbd339c48dbc6b33f5f5669e70f294c9082c8","tid":2246431,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T05:13:01.000Z","msg":"利物浦名宿巴恩斯（John Barnes）認為，雖然麥佳亞（Harry Maguire）如今飽受批評，但英格蘭中堅裡比他強的還真沒有幾個。<br />\n<br />\n　　「評判麥佳亞，不應該考慮曼聯買他的價格，因為這是他無法控制的，」巴恩斯說，「可能在英超中，他經歷了糟糕的幾星期，但這就是足球。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴恩斯觀點<br />\n　　「麥佳亞是這個國家最好的中堅，這是毫無疑問的，英格蘭隊裡有誰比他強？我看不到，祖-高美斯（Joe Gomez）和戴亞（Eric Dier），我看未必比他好。高迪為英格蘭踢了一場好球，但如果麥佳亞身體沒問題，高迪還能打主力嗎？我嚴重懷疑。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　「曼聯為他耗資8000萬英鎊，這不意味著他就是世界最佳中堅，這只是當時通貨膨脹的價格導致，但毫無疑問，在這個位置上，他是英格蘭最佳之一。」<br />\n<br />\n　　（彼特洛赫里）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/12290976/1/20201016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.soccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F12290976%2F1%2F20201016&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=5a6f325a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/12290976/1/20201016</a>"},{"pid":"ef08136e5e9cf91f58536458a79da545c384d638","tid":2246431,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T05:15:38.000Z","msg":"Smalling 都好過佢啦"},{"pid":"b2165451e46704647c788111778e5f487118758e","tid":2246431,"uid":186431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T05:23:41.000Z","msg":"evans都勁過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/handup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc304bac027d98d018c5468f4b2b7bc4b7c8cef2","tid":2246431,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b2165451e46704647c788111778e5f487118758e","tid":2246431,"uid":186431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T05:23:41.000Z","msg":"evans都勁過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/handup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T05:24:40.000Z","msg":"holdin